              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "An analytical model to predict the non-Rutherford",
                "threshold energy of scattering."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Experimental and theoretical non-Rutherford",
                "threshold energies for elastic scattering",
                "the ratios of 12-C, 14-N, and 16-O ion scattering",
                "yields from zinc and gold were measured and observed",
                "constant over the present energy and angular intervals.",
                " Rutherford Scattering from zinc was thus verified."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A Zn-S samples (40-50 mu-gramm/cm**2) with natural",
                "isotopic abundances on carbon and silicon substrates",
                "were used for cross section measurements.",
                "Spectra taken from targets of the substrate materials",
                "were normalized to correspond to the same ion dose as",
                "the Zn-S spectra.  The normalized spectra were",
                "subtracted from the Zn-S spectra to determine the areas",
                "of the sulfur and zinc peaks."
              ]
            }
          ],
